                  {
                    "chance": 2,
                    "verb": "wait",
                    "details": {
                      "text": "\"The warden usually makes his rounds several times a day. If you mean to ambush him, though, you may need to quietly hide in a corner,\" Mr Wheatfur suggests. \"Or else you could go looking for him.\""
                    }
